y.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.5736,"vote_count":4041,"poster_path":"/xXxuJPNUDZ0vjsAXca0O5p3leVB.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-19","vote_average":7.401,"backdrop_path":"/x7y8ezKtU1vRInk0dmbvDoKgJ8u.jpg","original_title":"As Good as It Gets","original_language":"en"},{"id":38408,"adult":false,"title":"Life As We Know It","video":false,"overview":"After a disastrous first date for caterer Holly and network sports director Messer, all they have in common is a dislike for each other and their love for their goddaughter Sophie. But when they suddenly become all Sophie has in this world, Holly and Messer must set their differences aside. Juggling careers and social calendars, they'll have to find common ground while living under the same roof.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1995,"vote_count":3243,"poster_path":"/zLzS2aOqKsS0QvEaY6SfBw4VBqh.jpg","release_date":"2010-10-02","vote_average":6.903,"backdrop_path":"/gfIARgK82GxXnPeBvAXDVBCzw61.jpg","original_title":"Life As We Know It","original_language":"en"},{"id":1197306,"adult":false,"title":"A Working Man","video":false,"overview":"Levon Cade left behind a decorated military career in the black ops to live a simple life working construction. But when his boss's daughter, who is like family to him, is taken by human traffickers, his search to bring her home uncovers a world of corruption far greater than he ever could have imagined.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.6703,"vote_count":1786,"poster_path":"/6FRFIogh3zFnVWn7Z6zcYnIbRcX.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-26","vote_average":6.686,"backdrop_path":"/fTrQsdMS2MUw00RnzH0r3JWHhts.jpg","original_title":"A Working Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":926393,"adult":false,"title":"The Equalizer 3","video":false,"overview":"Robert McCall finds himself at home in Southern Italy but he discovers his friends are under the control of local crime bosses. As events turn deadly, McCall knows